---

<section class="py-24 px-6 relative">
  <!-- Diagonal accent line -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[rgba(var(--color-accent-rgb),0.15)] to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="section-badge">
        <span class="section-badge-dot"></span>
        Philosophy
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-theme-primary">
        A manifesto for<br /><span class="gradient-text">tool ownership</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="manifesto-card">
      <div class="manifesto-grid">
        <!-- Left: What we reject -->
        <div>
          <div class="manifesto-label-group">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" class="text-red-400"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg>
            <p class="manifesto-label text-red-400/70">We reject</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="manifesto-list">
            <li class="manifesto-item reject"><span>Subscriptions on top of API costs</span></li>
            <li class="manifesto-item reject"><span>Middlemen marking up your tokens</span></li>
            <li class="manifesto-item reject"><span>Forked editors pretending to be new</span></li>
            <li class="manifesto-item reject"><span>Vendor lock-in to one AI provider</span></li>
            <li class="manifesto-item reject"><span>Your code going through someone else&apos;s servers</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Divider -->
        <div class="manifesto-divider">
          <div class="divider-vs">vs</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: What we believe -->
        <div>
          <div class="manifesto-label-group">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" class="text-[#28c840]"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <p class="manifesto-label text-[#28c840]">We believe in</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="manifesto-list">
            <li class="manifesto-item believe"><span>Molt Code is free &mdash; no strings attached</span></li>
            <li class="manifesto-item believe"><span>Direct API access with your keys</span></li>
            <li class="manifesto-item believe"><span>Purpose-built from scratch &mdash; not a forked editor</span></li>
            <li class="manifesto-item believe"><span>Use any AI provider &mdash; or all of them</span></li>
            <li class="manifesto-item believe"><span>Developers should own their tools completely</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Punchy quote -->
    <div class="quote-block">
      <div class="quote-mark">&ldquo;</div>
      <blockquote>
        If you&apos;re spending $200+ on API costs monthly,<br class="hidden md:block" />
        why pay another subscription on top?
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding: 0.375rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    background: rgba(var(--color-accent-rgb), 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--color-accent-rgb), 0.15);
  }

  .section-badge-dot {
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .manifesto-card {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }

  .manifesto-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .manifesto-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .manifesto-divider {
      height: 1px !important;
      width: 100% !important;
    }
    .manifesto-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  .manifesto-divider {
    width: 1px;
    align-self: stretch;
    background: var(--color-border);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .divider-vs {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    font-size: 0.625rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    opacity: 0.4;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    padding: 0.5rem 0.25rem;
  }

  .manifesto-label-group {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .manifesto-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .manifesto-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .manifesto-item {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .manifesto-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.55em;
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .manifesto-item.reject::before { background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4); }
  .manifesto-item.believe::before { background: rgba(40, 200, 64, 0.6); }

  .manifesto-item.reject span {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .manifesto-item.believe span {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .quote-block {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .quote-mark {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.15;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: -1.5rem;
  }

  .quote-block blockquote {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    opacity: 0.8;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .quote-block blockquote {
      font-size: 1.625rem;
    }
  }
</style>
